OL,3,CFriends say innocent bystander killed
OL,4,Coutside Sheffield bar had 'purest
OL,5,Cheart'
OL,7,FThe friend and cousin of a 30-year-old
OL,8,Finnocent bystander shot and killed in
OL,9,FSheffield have told Good Morning
OL,10,FBritain it is the "stuff of
OL,11,Fnightmares".
OL,13,FShanice Brookes was enjoying a night
OL,14,Fout with friends on West Street in the
OL,15,Fcity centre when she was caught in the
OL,16,Fline of fire in the early hours of
OL,17,Fbank holiday Monday. She later died in
OL,18,Fhospital.
OL,26,@rD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
