OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780049133
OL,3,CFriends say innocent bystander killed
OL,4,Coutside Sheffield bar had 'purest
OL,5,Cheart'
OL,7,FHer friend K-cee Cooper-Foster, whose
OL,8,Fchildren Shanice was godmother to, had
OL,9,Fbeen with her just hours before.
OL,11,F"She should have been coming back home
OL,12,Fto us and now we're never going to see
OL,13,Fher again," she said.
OL,15,FSpeaking alongside Shanice's cousin,
OL,16,FTyler-Jay Reid, they described the mum
OL,17,Fof one as "one of a kind".
OL,19,F"She had the purest heart and was the
OL,20,Fbest mum to her son anyone could ask
OL,21,Ffor," said Ms Cooper-Foster.
OL,26,@sD@AOUyD@KOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
