OL,3,CFriends say innocent bystander killed
OL,4,Coutside Sheffield bar had 'purest
OL,5,Cheart'
OL,7,FA man and a woman have since been
OL,8,Fcharged in connection with her death.
OL,10,FJemele Rhone, aged 30, of Outram Road,
OL,11,FSheffield, has been charged with
OL,12,Fmurder, possession of a firearm and
OL,13,Fpossession of criminal property.
OL,15,FDeiryen Dyce, aged 32, of Ellesmere
OL,16,FRoad North, Sheffield, has been
OL,17,Fcharged with assisting an offender,
OL,18,Fpossession of ammunition, possession
OL,19,Fof drugs with intent to supply,
OL,20,Fpossession of drugs and possession of
OL,21,Fcriminal property.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780049133
OL,3,CFriends say innocent bystander killed
OL,4,Coutside Sheffield bar had 'purest
OL,5,Cheart'
OL,7,FBoth have been remanded into custody
OL,8,Fahead of appearing at Sheffield
OL,9,FMagistrates' Court on Friday.
OL,11,FA 30-year-old man arrested on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of murder on Monday has now
OL,13,Fbeen released and is no longer being
OL,14,Ftreated as a suspect, South Yorkshire
OL,15,FPolice said.
OL,17,FMs Reid and Ms Cooper-Foster told GMB
OL,18,Fof the horror when they found out what
OL,19,Fhappened.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
