PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780049133
OL,3,CFriends say innocent bystander killed
OL,4,Coutside Sheffield bar had 'purest
OL,5,Cheart'
OL,7,F"She's gone out for a birthday
OL,8,Fcelebration. She's gone to let her
OL,9,Fhair down like any 30-year-old would,"
OL,10,Fsaid Ms Reid.
OL,12,F"She's been just an innocent person
OL,13,Fwho's just been in the wrong place at
OL,14,Fthe wrong time. It could happen to
OL,15,Fanyone. Anyone's daughter, anyone's
OL,16,Ffriend, anyone's family, and I would
OL,17,Fnot want anyone to go through what
OL,18,Fwe're going to have right now."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUzD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
