OL,3,CFriends say innocent bystander killed
OL,4,Coutside Sheffield bar had 'purest
OL,5,Cheart'
OL,7,FMs Brookes leaves behind a ten-year-
OL,8,Fold son, whom she had been due to take
OL,9,Fto the Arsenal victory parade this
OL,10,Fweekend, but who will now grow up
OL,11,Fwithout his mother.
OL,13,F"She's so selfless, she's not even a
OL,14,Fmassive football fan, but she was
OL,15,Fputting it aside for her son, and she
OL,16,Fwas going to take him to the
OL,17,FEmirates," said Ms Reid.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780049133
OL,3,CFriends say innocent bystander killed
OL,4,Coutside Sheffield bar had 'purest
OL,5,Cheart'
OL,7,F"She was so excited about going and he
OL,8,Fwas so excited to go down and
OL,9,Fsomething like that has now been
OL,10,Fripped apart from him."
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FMs Cooper-Foster and Ms Reid have set
OL,18,Fup a GoFundMe page to raise money for
OL,19,FShanice's funeral as well as her son's
OL,20,Ffuture.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
