OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1780049133
OL,3,CFriends say innocent bystander killed
OL,4,Coutside Sheffield bar had 'purest
OL,5,Cheart'
OL,7,F"We want to raise awareness, we want
OL,8,Fto do the best we can and push this
OL,9,FGoFundMe because we want her to have
OL,10,Fan amazing send off, but we also want
OL,11,Fto invest in the family and his
OL,12,Ffuture," Ms Reid said.
OL,14,F"It's not going to make it better, but
OL,15,Fwe can at least help give him a head
OL,16,Fstart and the future that he needs,"
OL,17,Fsaid Ms Cooper-Foster. "She would be
OL,18,Fdoing exactly the same for us."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUyD@XOUzD@_O]
